Summary: Star like object moving in the sky.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was walking out to my car to go to work it was about 6:00 am. I looked up at the sky like I always do and I saw this bight star looking thing flying south. It had no blinking lights, no sound at all and was moving faster than a plane would. I've seen this before and I know its not a plane I live by an airport and see planes all the time, this object was nowhere close to a plane.
